author: rhuijben
msg: As a tiny step towards fixing issue 3899 (auto resolve for wc-wc copies/moves),
move the code that performs a working copy move operation into libsvn_wc.
(Post 1.7 this will also help in supporting the recording of file moves).

author: mgrigorov
msg: WICKET-3757 Image always noncaching when included in ajax request. However, sometimes caching image is desirable.
Add #shouldAddAntiCacheParameter() which by default adds the parameter for Ajax requests.
The user can override it and chnage the check with his own.
